Heart Association, low calorie, restricted

01:07:41.400 --> 01:07:47.380
diet. So one diet, you cut fat. You cut saturated
fat. You cut calories. You're eating like,

01:07:47.380 --> 01:07:52.189
skinless chicken breast and lettuce. And the
