01:08:03.653 --> 01:08:08.390
But when the trials are done, what you find
is not only the people on the high fat diet,

01:08:08.390 --> 01:08:13.680
ad lib the eat as much as you want diet, weigh
less. Even though they're told they could

01:08:13.680 --> 01:08:18.440
eat as much as they want, their heart disease
risk profile factors improve. And this is

01:08:18.440 --> 01:08:21.089
what actually got me into this subject.

01:08:21.089 --> 01:08:25.750
