01:19:38.670 --> 01:19:44.170
it up: Low Fat versus Low Carb. And they left
out the crucial ingredient, which is one diet

01:19:44.170 --> 01:19:48.010
restricts calories and the other diet doesn't,
which is the ingredient that tells you you're

01:19:48.010 --> 01:19:49.960
paradigm might be wrong. OK.

