01:23:59.200 --> 01:24:02.930
have recently suggested that women typically
will recover better when they eat carbs after

01:24:02.930 --> 01:24:05.331
a meal too. And how that fits into all this.

01:24:05.331 --> 01:24:09.710
&gt;&gt;Gary Taubes: The question is about how,
what about athletics and endurance exercise.

01:24:09.710 --> 01:24:14.280
Don't you need the carbohydrates? Aren't they
crucial? [pause]

01:24:14.280 --> 01:24:21.890
This is not my area of expertise and I was
